Package resort

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivitiesController
    The activities controller is used by the guest to book activities during their resort stay.
    AvailableRoomsController
    The available rooms controller is shown to the user and displays the available rooms for the dates selected and the prices for those rooms.
    BlackOutDriver
    The blackout driver class is a class used to generate the values in the blackout tab for the manager view.
    CheckoutController
    The checkout controller is where the customer goes to checkout and leave guest feedback for the resort.
    CreateAccountController
    The create account controller gathers the guest's details and plugs them into the customer database.
    CurrentGuestController
    The current guest controller allows the user to login with their last name and phone number to book activities and other things.
    CurrentGuestOptionsController
    The current guest options controller shows the available options to the guest logged in.
    CustomerDriver
    The customer driver class is used to gather the data to populate the manager view customer information table view.
    DiningController
    The dining controller shows the guest the available places to dine at the resort.
    EmployeeDriver
    The employee driver class is used to create new employees in the manager view screen.
    GuestFeedbackController
    The guest feedback controller is used to gather the guest's feedback.
    HomeController
    The home controller displays the home page to the user.
    Main
    The main class of the project.
    ManagerDriver
    The manager driver class is used to setup the table view for the financial reports.
    ManagerLoginController
    The manager login screen allows the manager to login to the manager view screen.
    ManagerOverviewController
    The ManagerOverviewController corresponds to all items on the manager_overview.fxml file
    NewGuestController
    The new guest controller displays the date pickers and number of guests for their reservation.
    PaymentController
    The payment controller is used to gather the payment information from the guest and confirm their visit.
    SpecialRequestsController
    The special requests controller allows the user to request things from the front office.
